Release testing checklist. Successful installs should be reported with the
release candidate for each of the following before release.
							pass/fail (details)
i386
	netinst cd install taking the defaults
	businesscard cd install taking the defaults	
	floppy + cd install				
	floppy + network install			
	netboot install					
	pcmcia network install (any boot media)		
	lvm install					
	software raid install				
	32 mb ram install				
	48 mb ram install				
	2.6 install					
	2.6 pcmcia install				
	2.6 lvm install					
	2.6 software raid install			

